LearnWithZia
LearnWithZia is an online learning platform that offers a variety of free courses in subjects like programming, design, and digital marketing. The website is designed to help users enhance their skills through easily accessible resources.

Table of Contents
Features
Technologies Used
Installation
Usage
Contributing
License
Features
Course Catalog: Explore a wide range of online courses.
Search Functionality: Easily search for courses by keywords.
Filters: Filter courses by category, level, and duration.
Responsive Design: Optimized for both desktop and mobile devices.
Frequently Asked Questions: Get answers to common queries.
Technologies Used
HTML5: For the structure of the website.
CSS3: For styling the website, including animations.
Bootstrap 4: For responsive design and UI components.
JavaScript: For dynamic interactions and filtering functionality.
Installation
Clone the repository:

bash
Copy code
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/LearnWithZia.git
Navigate to the project directory:

bash
Copy code
cd LearnWithZia
Open index.html in your preferred web browser.

Usage
Upon opening the application, you will see the home page with the course catalog.
Use the filter options on the left sidebar to narrow down courses based on category, level, and duration.
Utilize the search bar to find specific courses.
Click on any course to learn more about it or to enroll.
